{"title":"景颇女儿上大学（图片）","authors":["程犁"],"dates":[{"year":1972,"month":12,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"景颇女儿上大学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"程犁油画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"景颇族新民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口弦弹得百鸟争鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌唤来满天彩云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木玎进京上大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山寨寨都欢腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿爸送木玎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福热泪满腮滚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妹送木玎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的攀枝花表深情；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿弟送木玎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高唱《我爱北京天安门》……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老支书送木玎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着朝阳出山林；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一程山路一席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句话儿重千斤："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“木玎，路上山高水又远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你千万莫要迷路径！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木玎点头微微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一字一字吐出唇："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“出山哪怕路艰险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里有颗北斗星！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}